-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32753,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/12\/jannah-gold-silver-pearls\/","url_meta":{"origin":31867,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Gold, silver, and pearl wonders in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, in Paradise are two gardens with silver vessels and two gardens with golden vessels. Nothing comes between its people looking upon their Lord but a curtain of majesty over His face in the Garden of Eden. In\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37915,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/23\/rivers-in-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":31867,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Rivers of water, milk, honey, and wine in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Haydah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, in Paradise there is a sea of water, a sea of honey, a sea of milk, and a sea of wine, and thereafter they branch into rivers.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2571 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20836,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/08\/17\/father-middle-door-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":31867,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Parents: Father is middle gate of Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 17, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe father is the middle of the gates of Paradise. If you wish, you can squander this gate or keep to it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1900 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u064e\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31702,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/souls-of-martyrs-green-birds\/","url_meta":{"origin":31867,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Shuhada: Souls of martyrs alive in green birds of Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the souls of martyrs are in green birds, hanging from the fruits of Paradise, or the trees of Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1641 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u064